OL,3,CGreat-grandfather from Margate to walk
OL,4,C90 miles in 90th birthday charity
OL,5,Ceffort
OL,7,FITV News Meridian's John Ryall caught
OL,8,Fup with Derrick before his challenge
OL,10,FA great-grandfather will walk 90 miles
OL,11,Fto mark his 90th birthday in aid of
OL,12,Fraising money for a vital charity.
OL,14,FDerrick Downs, from Margate, has set
OL,15,Fhimself a #9,000 target to support
OL,16,FOasis, an organisation which provides
OL,17,Fhelp to survivors of domestic abuse.
OL,19,FIt has taken Derrick months of
OL,20,Ftraining to physically prepare himself
OL,21,Ffor his milestone birthday challenge.
