OL,3,CGreat-grandfather from Margate to walk
OL,4,C90 miles in 90th birthday charity
OL,5,Ceffort
OL,7,FDerrick said, "I had been thinking
OL,8,Fabout what I should do to celebrate my
OL,9,F90th birthday. And I came up with this
OL,10,Fbright idea of walking 90 miles in
OL,11,Fnine days. But of course, the nearer I
OL,12,Fget, the less bright it seems.
OL,14,F"Oasis not only work in Sandwich and
OL,15,FDover, but they also work in North
OL,16,FKent and Medway so that really set the
OL,17,Froute. It's why in Dover, going to
OL,18,FFolkestone and then walking to Medway
OL,19,Ftowns back through to Sittingbourne
OL,20,FFaversham, along to Herne Bay back to
OL,21,FMargate."
