OL,5,Ceffort
OL,7,FThe former RAF veteran has been
OL,8,Finvolved with Oasis for a quarter of a
OL,9,Fcentury and was once a chair of
OL,10,Ftrustees for the charity.
OL,12,FJuliette Lyons said, "What Derek's
OL,13,Fdoing is incredible. He's been
OL,14,Fsupporting Oasis for a long time now,
OL,15,Fand I think we're all in awe of the
OL,16,Ffact that he's using this milestone to
OL,17,Fmake a real difference.
