OL,3,CGreat-grandfather from Margate to walk
OL,4,C90 miles in 90th birthday charity
OL,5,Ceffort
OL,7,F"I'm a third of his age and I
OL,8,Fcertainly don't do the amount of steps
OL,9,Fthat he's been doing. We're just so
OL,10,Fgrateful and we're really rooting for
OL,11,Fhim."
OL,13,FEach day, Derrick will walk 10 miles
OL,14,Fover a nine day period, when he sets
OL,15,Foff January 22nd.
OL,17,FThe route will start in Folkestone and
OL,18,Fend in Margate, taking in Maidstone,
OL,19,FSittingbourne, Whitstable and Herne
OL,20,FBay along the way.
